    dc:creator "Davies, Kerrie A.; Taylor, Gary S.; Nelson, Leigh A.; Yeates, David; Giblin-Davis, Robin M." ;
    dc:date "2014" ;
    dc:title "Nematodes from galls on Myrtaceae. VI. Fergusobia from galls on Angophora in Australia, with description of F. colbrani n. sp. and key" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.225346>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.225352>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.225348>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.225353> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.225346>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Habitus drawings of Fergusobia spp. collected from Angophora spp.: A, F. floribundae from shoot bud galls on A. floribunda; B, F. pimpamensis from shoot bud galls on A.? woodsiana; C, morphospecies A from ‘ leafy’ leaf bud galls on A. floribunda; D, morphospecies B from ‘ stem’ galls on A. floribunda; E, F. colbrani n. sp. from leaf galls on A. floribunda. Scale bars = 50 Μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/225346/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.225352>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Fergusobia / Fergusonina galls from Angophora floribunda: A, Terminal leaf bud gall; B, ‘ stem’ gall; C, D, E, ‘ moss’ gall; F, spheroid leaf gall. Scale bars = 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/225352/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.225348>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Anterior region of Fergusobia spp. collected from Angophora spp.: A, F. floribundae from shoot bud galls on A. floribunda; B, F. pimpamensis from shoot bud galls on A.? woodsiana; C, morphospecies A from ‘ leafy’ leaf bud galls on A. floribunda; D, morphospecies B from moss ‘ stem’ galls on A. floribunda; E, F. colbrani n. sp. from spheroid leaf galls on A. floribunda; F, morphospecies B from smooth ‘ stem’ galls on A. floribunda. Left – right: A – B parthenogenetic female, infective female, male; C – F parthenogenetic female, male. Scale bar = 5 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/225348/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.225353>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Dorsal shield of L 3 Fergusonina larvae from spheroid leaf galls on Angophora floribunda, associated with F. colbrani n. sp. (automontage image). Scale bar = 0.15 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/225353/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

